     <text:p text:style-name="P96"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-15"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Începe!...#cite_ref-1" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T17">↑</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T23"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">Ipistat - subcomisar</text:span></text:p>
    </text:list-item>
    <text:list-item>
     <text:p text:style-name="P97"><text:bookmark text:name="cite_note-24"/><text:a xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="https://ro.wikisource.org/wiki/Începe!...#cite_ref-2" text:style-name="Internet_20_link" text:visited-style-name="Visited_20_Internet_20_Link"><text:span text:style-name="T17">↑</text:span></text:a><text:span text:style-name="T23"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="T18">Autorul face aluzie la afirmația lui Arhimede: „Dați-mi un punct fix în univers, și cu o pârghie pot mișca pământul”.</text:span></text:p>
